  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'it''s freezing out here

    but so calm

    the forest is closing in
    behind us

    I can hear the river

    that once swallowed you


    now it''s
    asking

    "touch me with your hand"

    reminding me

    of the rose

    raised
    from stone

    cut off by words

    and turned into prose

    by my desire'
